# Smart Voice Assistant 🎙️

A Python-based voice-activated desktop assistant with a dark-mode GUI.

## Features
- Voice command recognition with ambient noise adjustment
- Open Chrome, Notepad, Spotify via voice
- Google search, WhatsApp messaging, Email automation
- Wikipedia fallback for unknown queries
- Multithreaded GUI using CustomTkinter

## Tech Stack
Python, SpeechRecognition, pyttsx3, CustomTkinter, 
Gmail SMTP, pywhatkit, Wikipedia API

## Setup
1. Clone the repo
2. pip install -r requirements.txt
3. Create a .env file (see .env.example)
4. Run: python assistant.py

## Commands
| Say | Action |
|-----|--------|
| "open chrome" | Opens browser |
| "search ..." | Google search |
| "send whatsapp" | WhatsApp message |
| "email" | Send email |
| "time" | Current time |
| "exit" | Close assistant |
